cal/Microsoft/Windows/INetCache/Content.Outlook/AX6XEHEU/Introduction_Lahoud_190822%20-%20ARABIC%20online.docx#_ftnref3\" name=\"_ftn3\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span dir=\"LTR\"><!--[if !supportFootnotes]--><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">[3]</span></span><!--[endif]--></span></span></a><span dir=\"LTR\"> </span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Simplified Arabic\",serif\">كما\r\nورد في اليونور ويلدبيرغر:</span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Simplified Arabic\",serif\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span> “Indigenous Australian Art in Practice and\r\nTheory,” Coolabah 10</span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Simplified Arabic\",serif\"><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span> (2013) ص 204.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"ftn4\">\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><a href=\"file:///C:/Users/Admin/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/INetCache/Content.Outlook/AX6XEHEU/Introduction_Lahoud_190822%20-%20ARABIC%20online.docx#_ftnref4\" name=\"_ftn4\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span dir=\"LTR\"><!--[if !supportFootnotes]--><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-theme-font:\